  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.dft.gov.uk/news/press-releases/dft-press-20120308a/"&gt;Ending inflation-busting rail fare rises press release, 8 March 2012&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
